## 🛠️ Daily Commands Cheat Sheet

```bash
# Morning sync (every day)
cd d:\sem4\openalgo
git checkout main
git fetch upstream
git merge upstream/main
git push origin main

# Start today's work
git checkout -b <branch-type>/<branch-name>

# Before committing
uv run ruff check . --fix
uv run pytest test/ -v --timeout=60

# Commit with conventional message
git add .
git commit -m "type: description (#issue)"

# Push and go to GitHub to create PR
git push origin <branch-name>
```

### Branch Naming Convention
```
test/conftest-fixtures          ← Day 1
test/place-order-service        ← Day 2  
docs/add-docstrings-database    ← Day 3
docs/add-docstrings-utils       ← Day 4
refactor/print-to-logger        ← Day 5
fix/docker-compose-volumes      ← Day 9
test/integration-test-harness   ← Days 20-21, 24
```

